Terribly noisy!!!!
Canâ€™t even consider that there are apartment buildings, elderly, families living across the sea who just want peace and quiet and yet they fly their airplanes and shoot things so loudly it shakes the balcony doors of my apartment!
Best school attended and taught at in my life. Lead by Example! Good memories, long and tiring days as cadet and instructor. Worthwhile and memorable.
Definitely not a place any parent will want their son to go.
